133	## 7. Sections
134	
135	### Section 1: Progress Chart
136	
137	**Description:** Line chart displaying weight over time with toggle options to filter by 1 week, 1 month, or all time.
138	
139	**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `Card` with a line chart widget (e.g., `fl_chart`)
140	
141	**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, 16dp corner radius.
142	
143	**Components:**
144	- Section header: "Weight Progress" (`headlineMedium`, 24sp)
145	- Toggle chips row: "1W" / "1M" / "All" — horizontally arranged, 8dp gap
146	  - Default selected: "1W"
147	  - Selected chip: `lavenderBloom` background at 15% opacity with `lavenderBloom` text
148	  - Unselected chip: `stone100` background, `stoneGrey` text
149	- Line chart:
150	  - X-axis: Date labels (formatted as "MMM d")
151	  - Y-axis: Weight in user's preferred unit (kg/lbs from `UserPreferences`)
152	  - Line color: `lavenderBloom`
153	  - Fill: Gradient from `lavenderBloom` at 20% opacity to transparent
154	  - Data points: Small dots, 4dp diameter
155	  - Grid lines: `mistyBorder` at 50% opacity
156	- Touch interaction: Show tooltip with exact value on tap/drag
157	
158	**Data Requirements:**
159	- `WeightEntry` list from `WeightEntryProvider`, filtered by selected time range
160	- `UserPreferences.units` for y-axis label formatting
161	
162	**Interactive Elements:**
163	- Tap toggle chip → re-render chart with filtered data
164	- Drag on chart → show tooltip with date and weight
165	
166	---
167	
168	### Section 2: Latest Entry Card
169	
170	**Description:** Prominent card showing today's weight entry with delta from the previous entry.
171	
172	**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `Card` with `Column` layout
173	
174	**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, 16dp corner radius.
175	
176	**Components:**
177	- Card background: `morningMist` (#FAFAFA), soft shadow
178	- "Today's Weight" label (`caption`, `stoneGrey`)
179	- Weight display: Large number (`displayLarge`, `deepGraphite`) with unit suffix ("kg" or "lbs")
180	- Delta row: Arrow icon + delta value + "from last entry"
181	  - Positive delta: `softCoral` text, up-arrow icon
182	  - Negative delta: `softMint` text, down-arrow icon
183	  - Zero delta: `stoneGrey` text, horizontal arrow
184	- Timestamp: "Logged at [time]" (`caption`, `stoneGrey`)
185	- Empty state: "No weight logged today" message with "Tap + to add" subtitle
186	
187	**Data Requirements:**
188	- Most recent `WeightEntry` from `WeightEntryProvider`
189	- Previous `WeightEntry` for delta calculation
190	- `UserPreferences.units` for unit display
191	
192	**Interactive Elements:**
193	- None (display-only card)
194	
195	---
196	
197	### Section 3: Nutrition Tips Card
198	
199	**Description:** Stage-specific nutrition tips based on the user's current pregnancy week, pulled from `WeekContent.nutritionTips`.
200	
201	**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `Card` with `Column` layout
202	
203	**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, 16dp corner radius. Background: `lavenderTint` for subtle differentiation.
204	
205	**Components:**
206	- Header row: "Nutrition Tips" (`titleMedium`) + week badge ("Week [N]" pill, `lavenderBloom` background, white text)
207	- Tip list: `BulletList` of 3-5 tip items from `WeekContent.nutritionTips`
208	- Each tip item: Small dot (blushRose) + tip text (`bodyMedium`)
209	- "Learn more" link/text button at bottom (optional for MVP)
210	
211	**Data Requirements:**
212	- `currentWeek` from `PregnancyProfileProvider`
213	- `WeekContent` entry for `currentWeek` from static catalog
214	- `nutritionTips: List<String>` field
215	
216	**Interactive Elements:**
217	- Tap card → expand to show full tips (if collapsed)
218	
219	---
