250	### Section 5 (Overlay): Add Weight Bottom Sheet
251	
252	**Description:** Form for logging a new weight entry.
253	
254	**Trigger:** Tap FAB `+`
255	
256	**Widget Type:** `showModalBottomSheet` with `SingleChildScrollView`
257	
258	**Layout:** Bottom sheet with 28dp top corner radius, handle bar, max 90% screen height.
259	
260	**Components:**
261	- Handle bar: 40dp wide, 4dp tall, centered, Stone 300 color
262	- Title: "Log Weight" (`titleLarge`)
263	- Weight input field: Numeric `TextField` with floating label "Weight", suffix for unit (kg/lbs)
264	- Date picker field: "Date" label with date display, tap → `showDatePicker`, defaults to today
265	- Notes field: Multi-line `TextField` with 56dp min height, hint "Add notes (optional)..."
266	- Action buttons: "Cancel" (text) and "Save" (primary pill button)
267	- Form validation: Weight value required and must be > 0, date must be today or in the past
