273	
274	### Section 6 (Overlay): Entry Detail/Edit Bottom Sheet
275	
276	**Description:** View, edit, or delete existing weight entry.
277	
278	**Trigger:** Long-press log list item
279	
280	**Components:**
281	- Header: Date (editable via date picker)
282	- Weight field (editable)
283	- Notes field (editable)
284	- Delete button: `softCoral` text button, triggers confirmation dialog
285	- "Save Changes" primary button
