291	---
292	
293	## 8. Data
294	
295	### Entity: WeightEntry
296	
297	| Field | Type | Required | Description |
298	|---|---|---|---|
299	| `id` | `String` (UUID) | Yes | Unique identifier |
300	| `date` | `DateTime` | Yes | Date of weight measurement |
301	| `value` | `double` | Yes | Weight value in user's preferred unit |
302	| `notes` | `String` | No | Optional notes about the entry |
303	
304	### Provider: WeightEntryProvider
305	
306	**State:**
307	- `entries: List<WeightEntry>` — all logged weight entries
308	- `selectedRange: ChartRange` — current chart filter (1W, 1M, All)
309	
310	**Methods:**
311	- `addEntry(value, date, notes)` — adds new weight entry
312	- `updateEntry(id, entry)` — modifies existing entry
313	- `deleteEntry(id)` — removes entry
314	- `getLatestEntry()` — returns most recent entry
315	- `getEntriesForRange(range)` — filters entries by time range
316	- `calculateDelta()` — returns difference between latest and previous entry
317	
318	**Computed:**
319	- `latestEntry` = entries sorted by date descending, first item
320	- `previousEntry` = entries sorted by date descending, second item (if exists)
321	- `delta` = latestEntry.value - previousEntry.value
322	
323	### Related Entities
324	
325	| Entity | Field Used | Source |
326	|---|---|---|
327	| `PregnancyProfile` | `currentWeek` | `PregnancyProfileProvider` |
328	| `WeekContent` | `nutritionTips` (keyed by week) | Static catalog |
329	| `UserPreferences` | `units` (kg/lbs) | `UserPreferencesProvider` |
330	
